'''Kneelers'''Â is a derogatory name used by theÂ [[Free Folk]] to describe people who live south of [[the Wall]]. In [[Westeros]] kneeling is an act of submission.&lt;ref&gt;[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VyG1rk1XgT4 Game of Thrones: Season 3 - Inside The Wildlings (HBO)]&lt;/ref&gt;

The Free Folk do not kneel for anyone, while the kneelers are subject to laws, lords and kings. The Free Folk view the kneelers as lacking freedom, whereas the people of the [[Seven Kingdoms]] view the &quot;wildlings&quot; as savage, lawless and uncivilized killers, rapists and thieves.
